.description
A powerful text editor with lots of features, some not found elsewhere.
Integrated Text oriented database, extensive formatting/printing functions,
macro language, Arexx-port, keyword indention, multiple blocks/marks,
key/menu macro recording, configurability for lot's of languages/compilers,
inumerable handy functions for programmers, user friendly interface.  
